news_header: Anora's CEO Jacek Pa.zka announces his resignation.
news_text: Jacek Pa.zka, the CEO of Anora, has informed the company's Board of Directors of his intention to resign. Anora, known for brands like Koskenkorva and Blossa, will begin the search for a new CEO. Pa.zka has been in the role for about a year, and the Koskenkorva factory is situated in South O.bothnia.
